title: Previewing Week 6 from Lawrence, KS
description:
Jen Lada, David Pollack, and Desmond Howard break down the undefeated Jayhawks as well as big conference games for a number of top-ranked teams. Plus, Pete Thamel joins the show to provide an injury update for the starting QB for Alabama.
